(99, 1, '2020-05-09 00:20:00', '2020-05-08 17:20:00', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>ÄÄng nháº­p vÃ o Google Classroom</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Truy cáº­p ÄÆ°á»ng dáº«n <a href=\"https://classroom.google.com\"><strong>https://classroom.google.com</strong></a> vÃ  chá»n <strong>Go to Classroom</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ÄÄng nháº­p vÃ o báº±ng tÃ i khoáº£n Google</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NgoÃ i ra náº¿u báº¡n ÄÃ£ ÄÄng nháº­p sáºµn vÃ o Google thÃ¬ khi truy cáº­p trang web sáº½ hiá»n ra báº£ng xÃ¡c nháº­n tham gia Google Classroom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ÄÄng nháº­p thÃ nh cÃ´ng sáº½ hiá»n ra giao diá»n nhÆ° hÃ¬nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Tham gia lá»p há»c</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CÃ³ 2 cÃ¡ch Äá» tham gia lá»p há»c</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CÃ¡ch 1:</strong> Tham gia báº±ng cÃ¡ch nháº­p mÃ£ lá»p há»c mÃ  giÃ¡o viÃªn cung cáº¥p.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nháº¥n vÃ o dáº¥u + á» hÃ¬nh trÃªn Äá» nháº­p mÃ£ lá»p há»c</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Náº¿u cÃ³ lá»p há»c thÃ¬ báº¡n sáº½ ÄÆ°á»£c thÃªm thÃ nh cÃ´ng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CÃ¡ch 2:</strong> Nháº­n mail má»i tham gia lá»p há»c tá»« giÃ¡o viÃªn</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GiÃ¡o viÃªn sáº½ má»i sinh viÃªn tham gia lá»p há»c báº±ng cÃ¡ch gá»­i mail Äáº¿n sinh viÃªn, sinh viÃªn kiá»m mail Äá» tham gia lá»p há»c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi tham gia thÃ nh cÃ´ng ta sáº½ vÃ o ÄÆ°á»£c giao diá»n trang chÃ­nh cá»§a Classroom</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>á» má»¥c <strong>Luá»ng</strong> hiá»n thá» táº¥t cáº£ thÃ´ng tin mÃ  má»i thÃ nh viÃªn trong lá»p chia sáº» lÃªn Classroom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Báº¡n cÃ³ thá» chia sáº» báº±ng cÃ¡ch chá»n vÃ o khung âchia sáº» ÄÃ´i Äiá»u vá» lá»p há»câBáº¡n cÃ³ thá» chia sáº» thÃ´ng tin vÃ  ÄÄng táº£i thÃªm tá»p. HoÃ n thÃ nh báº±ng nÃºt <strong>ÄÄng</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Xem bÃ i táº­p vÃ  ná»p bÃ i cho giÃ¡o viÃªn</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Báº¡n cÃ³ thá» xem táº¥t cáº£ bÃ i táº­p ÄÃ£ upload lÃªn Classroom á» má»¥c <strong>BÃ i táº­p trÃªn lá»p</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Äá» xem bÃ i táº­p cÃ¡ nhÃ¢n cá»§a mÃ¬nh thÃ¬ chá»n <strong>Xem bÃ i táº­p cá»§a báº¡n</strong>. Má»t giao diá»n má»i hiá»n thá» toÃ n bá» nhá»¯ng bÃ i táº­p dÃ nh cho báº¡n vÃ  tÃ¬nh tráº¡ng ÄÃ£ ná»p hay chÆ°a</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Äá» hiá»n thá» chi tiáº¿t chÃºng ta nháº¥n vÃ o tá»«ng bÃ i táº­p Äá» xem chi tiáº¿t.Â </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ThÃªm file ÄÃ­nh kÃ¨m: Sinh viÃªn cÃ³ thá» gá»­i ná»i dung bÃ i ÄÄng dÆ°á»i dáº¡ng má»t táº­p tin ÄÃ­nh kÃ¨m tá»« mÃ¡y sinh viÃªn, hoáº·c tá»« Drive trong há»p thÆ° cá»§a sinh viÃªn. NgoÃ i ra sinh viÃªn cÃ³ thá» gá»­i má»t ná»i dung dÆ°á»i dáº¡ng video ÄÆ°á»£c thu hÃ¬nh sáºµn (ÄÆ°á»£c upload lÃªn Youtube) , hoáº·c má»t Äá»a chá» website liÃªn quan Äáº¿n bÃ i ÄÄng cá»§a mÃ¬nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi táº¡o xong sinh viÃªn nháº¥n <strong>ÄÄNG</strong> Äá» gá»­i ná»i dung cho cÃ¡c báº¡n trong lá»p.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hoáº·c sinh viÃªn cÅ©ng cÃ³ thá» thÃªm cÃ¡c nháº­n xÃ©t vá» bÃ i táº­p: nháº­n xÃ©t cÃ³ thá» lÃ  cÃ´ng khai náº¿u muá»n má»i ngÆ°á»i Äá»u Äá»c ÄÆ°á»£c hoáº·c lÃ  nháº­n xÃ©t riÃªng tÆ° Äá» giÃ¡o viÃªn cÃ³ thá» Äá»c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Há»§y ÄÄng kÃ½ lá»p há»c</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>VÃ¬ má»t lÃ½ do nÃ o ÄÃ³, cÃ³ thá» ÄÄng kÃ½ nháº§m,â¦ sinh viÃªn cáº§n há»§y lá»p há»c ÄÃ£ ÄÄng kÃ½. Äá» há»§y lá»p há»c, báº¡n cáº§n nháº¥n vÃ o biá»u tÆ°á»£ng <img width=\"33\" height=\"36\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/LddHj2PAqlZ4oAMXR6LD_24eIs3ZbUqNmf333WCJlipdKV3R3NzoEb2ceUJB3foh6RhJqc8TQJoluyo-XWiPbhdBnA60E3-4WPDhcYggNaCXZEHTrq-2awFlFtI3DLCApkGV3LxzzlH_JZt36A\"> á» trÃ¡i trÃªn cÃ¹ng cá»§a trang web vÃ  chá»n vÃ o <strong>Lá»p há»c</strong> Äá» trá» vá» danh sÃ¡ch cÃ¡c lá»p há»c ÄÃ£ tham gia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TÃ¬m Äáº¿n lá»p há»c muá»n há»§y chá»n vÃ o biá»u tÆ°á»£ng <img width=\"32\" height=\"46\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/34PWywFYhPXNpEL1pmwMBK_NSUE5Xv5BNQZCjLvTjROywWDyk3_rZY1zNiiC0Sofvk4-R_IGXBqreFFkBMyKE3BwKW4O0dYnyOXx4UaxF0_pXpCMojNpy1wldUeqgRn5WmqoE4WkXIBafft1-A\"> vÃ  chá»n <strong>Há»§y ÄÄng kÃ½</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Má»t thÃ´ng bÃ¡o sáº½ hiá»n lÃªn. Báº¡n nháº¥n <strong>Há»§y ÄÄng kÃ½</strong> Äá» xÃ¡c nháº­n rá»i khá»i lá»p há»c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Váº­y lÃ  báº¡n ÄÃ£ biáº¿t nhá»¯ng chá»©c nÄng cÅ©ng nhÆ° cÃ¡ch sá»­ dá»¥ng cÆ¡ báº£n nháº¥t vá»i Google Classroom rá»i Äáº¥y!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"right\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\"><strong>Thanh BÃ¹i</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'HÆ°á»ng Dáº«n Sá»­ Dá»¥ng Google Classroom Cho Sinh ViÃªn', 'HÆ°á»ng dáº«n sá»­ dá»¥ng cÃ¡c chá»©c n